d_stolen) == 20:\\n    print('\\\\nSUCCESS: All 20 rows match up to permutation and scaling.')\\nelse:\\n    print('\\\\nWARNING: Some rows did not match.')\\nEOF\\n\", \"duration\": 1.0}\n  ]\n}"
